Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiya, Scootaloo! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rainbow Dash fan\Nclub just decided
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,everypony's coming to see you\Nwhen the Wonderbolts' new tour
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,comes through Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's great that you guys\Nare going to the show, Scoot,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but I won't actually\Nbe performing in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Reservists aren't\Nin the show
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,unless one of the real\NWonderbolts can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably be working\Ncrowd control or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still gonna be\Nwearing a Wonderbolts uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A Reservist one, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. That's good\Nenough for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! Glad\Nwe found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:01:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you in the show when\Nwe get to Ponyville. Flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's only\Nin the Reserves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! You're finally\Na full-fledged Wonderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! Yeah!\NRainbow Dash! Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.90,0:01:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What\Nshe said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\Nby YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, anypony see my wing\Nbalm? I don't wanna be stiff
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when I show up at\NWonderbolt headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have time to tell us\Nwhat happened, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo yes, we must\Nknow every detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Start from when you were\Na foal and you first knew
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,your destiny was to\Nbecome a Wonderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not\Nmuch to tell, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Spitfire told me the\NWonderbolts need me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to go on tour with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how long you've been\Nwaiting for a spot to open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Fire Streak decided to\Nretire and teach full-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale Flight School will\Nprobably be churning out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderbolts with him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But guess who was at the\Ntop of the Reserve list?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh ooh! I know! Pick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you\Ndo now, Dashie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to report to\NWonderbolts Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,this afternoon. It's only\Ntwo days till tour starts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I need to learn\Nthe routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But we barely started your\Ncongratulation party!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even thought about\Nyour going away party yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, I'm not\Nleaving Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to\Ntrain for this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope everything\Ngoes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like an\Nawful lot of pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,having to learn\Neverything so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good luck, Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Luck? Save that\Nfor the rest of the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that my awesomeness has\Nfinally been recognized,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the other Wonderbolts\Nwill have to keep up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,or eat my cloud-trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony knows you're a\Ngreat flier, Rainbow Dash,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but so are the rest\Nof the Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be more\Nchallenging than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, do I show up\Nwearing sunglasses or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunglasses are\Nautomatically cool,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but anypony can\Nput them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'd stand out\Nmore if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Team briefings are\Nevery morning at--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,--oh seven twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there were twenty\Nponies in the original
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,EUP Guard that became\Nthe Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. And I know you've\Nseen the Academy bunks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but these are the official\NWonderbolts' barracks--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--built by Admiral\NFairweather himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget rule\Nnumber one, newbie:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,always check both ways\Nbefore crossing the runway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh sure, but nopony\Nelse is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They will be. And most\Nof the Wonderbolts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,like to make a flashy\Nentrance, so stay alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Is that\NGeneral Flash's cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And the original crest with\Nthe Wonderbolts motto on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Altius volantis."\N"Soaring higher!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,WOW! I mean... cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, newbie, we've got\Na show in two days,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which means you've gotta\Nhustle your haunches
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to learn this routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got five minutes to\Nget dressed and get outside
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to meet the rest of the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am! I'll have\Nall the moves down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope so. We're\Nall expecting you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to make quite\Nan impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookin' good! OK, you're about\Nto take your first flight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,as an actual Wonderbolt.\NNo pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just gotta go out there and\Nknock 'em off their hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, Wonderbolts, get\Nready to meet your most
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,awesome member ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Most awesome\Nentrance by a newbie ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,More like Rainbow Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, flight school. Get\Nready for Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whooooooooa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,More like Rainbow Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Crash, Rainbow Crash,\NRainbow Crash, Rainbow Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You guys buzzed\Nme on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite. You forgot\Nrule number one, newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Always check both ways\Nbefore crossing the runway."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I was just...\Ntesting you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, nopony got hurt\Nand we've got a lot to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's forget about\Nthis and get flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Classic rookie move, Rainbow\NCrash. That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher, Crash! You're\Nbreaking formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Check your nine, Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tighter, Crash! Get in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's not Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! Coulda fooled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Crash, I know it\Nwas a tough day today,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't worry, you'll\Nget the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough day? Please. If I can\Npull off a Sonic Rainboom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can learn this routine. I'll\Nhave it down cold tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably even come up with\Na couple of improvements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're\Nstill here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Did you want\Nsome ideas on how
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to make the show\Nextra awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite. I know you've\Nbeen a Reservist for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Bolts have a\Nfew of their own rules
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you might not know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like worst flier\Nof the day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,has to clean up the\Nwhole compound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Better get to it, Crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's not Crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray, Rainbow Dash!\NOur favorite Wonderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We know you're probably\Ntired, Rainbow Dash,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but Pinkie wanted to\Nthrow you a real party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Best Day EVER party!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was\Nsomething, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't wait\Nto hear all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd love to\Ntell you. I really would.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm pretty beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, from all the\Nexcitement of my big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, is something\Nwrong, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What could be wrong? I'm\Nfinally a Wonderbolt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,which means everything has to\Nbe totally perfectly awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, something is wrong.\NWhat happened, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, maybe some of the\NWonderbolts started calling me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Rainbow Crash".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Isn't that the\Nsame terrible nickname
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,those bullies in flight\Nschool used to call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they call you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I, kinda, sorta\Nfell into a garbage can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look at the\Nbright side!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At least they didn't\Ncall you Rainbow Trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you started off\Non the wrong hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet every new Wonderbolt\Nhas a tough first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um-hum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What you need is to find a\Npositive way to stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you're known\Nfor something else,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that nasty old nickname\Nwill be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you think of the\NWonderbolts like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a team, but we all stand\Nout in different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I'm gonna stand out\Nin a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Rainbow Crash,\Nhello, Captain Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's ready for a fantastic day\Nof flying? I know I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't be more excited
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for the big show tomorrow. Are\Nyou guys excited? I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm always excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Some ponies even call\Nme "Dynamic Dash"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm so full of\Nenergy all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Wonderbolts don't\Nget excited, Crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta keep a level\Nhead to fly the way we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth of the matter is,\Nyou should be excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the dream of near every\Nlittle Pegasus pony
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to grow up and fly\Nwith the Wonderbolts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and here you all are doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,True. Go ahead and call me\N"Forthright Filly"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want, but she-ucks, I\Nlike to tell it like it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I believe a pony oughta\Nappreciate hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,paying off like this because\Nbeing a Wonderbolt
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is somethin' special.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} We know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I was just reading\Nabout how dihedral wing angles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,can help increase stability\Nin banking turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me think that\Npre-flight checklists
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,could really help\Nincrease our efficiency,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so I went ahead and made\Nthem for everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always finding so much\Ninteresting information
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in books. In fact, a lot of\Nponies call me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Reading Rainboom."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know how\Nwings work, newbie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and we already have checklists!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get off the runway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.\NI was just trying to help
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,because I care about all of the\NWonderbolts oh so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesiree, just call\Nme "Care Mare."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, but if you're busy now, I\Ncan just come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, you know, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I must tell you how much I\Njust love these uniforms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, ever since I was a foal,\NI've admired the mixture
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of bold lines and\Nclassic contours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't call me "Rainbow\NFash" for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Fash" is for fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why you're\Nacting like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but you need to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just, you know,\Ntrying to show everypony
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,all the awesome ways I can\Ncontribute to the Bolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're excited to find\Nyour place on the team,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but just focus on the\Nroutine for now, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this will\Nhelp motivate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Crash?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you just put\Nmy regular name on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how it\Nworks around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have our nicknames on our\Njackets. Right, Clipper?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Clipper?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's official. Welcome to\Nthe Wonderbolts, Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't come up with\Nsomething unforgettable
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to add to the routine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be Rainbow Crash\Nfor the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I'm almost as\Nexcited as Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see Rainbow\NDash's first performance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,as an honest to\Ngoodness Wonderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope there's\Ncotton candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We should all remember\Nto be extra supportive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for Rainbow Dash, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent point. It's simply\Ndreadful that she's had
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,such a rough start after\Nfinally achieving her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash is a pretty\Nresilient pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's shaken\Noff her tough first day
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and turned it around by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of - hey Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, perfect! Hey, can\NI borrow Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just\Nneeded some help
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and figured the president of\Nthe Rainbow Dash fan club
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,was the right pony for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the Wonderbolt\NReserves were here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, they're all busy doing\Nofficial Reserves stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry, with\NScootaloo's help,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,everything's gonna be awesome.\NBetter than awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Does-does that mean practice\Nwent well yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we doing up here,\NRainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need a small\Nfavor from you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that's really gonna make this\Nshow something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the Wonderbolts are going\Nto fly over this ridge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,right before the\Nfinale of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fly by last and\Nwhen I signal you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you zip up the ramp\Non your scooter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and kick the storm\Ncloud into my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That kick will shoot\Noff a lightning bolt
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,right behind me, making\Nme look totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll do some\Nincredible Rainbow Dash flying
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with it, to create the\Ncoolest, show-stoppingest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,lightning-tastic light show\Nanypony has ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna\Nbe so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And no pony will ever call me\N"Rainbow Crash" after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gotta go! Be ready for\Nme, OK, Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mares and gentlecolts, fillies\Nand foals of all ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,look to the skies and\Nprepare to be awestruck
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,by the incredible flying\Nprowess of the Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Spike and Pinkie Pie\Nare done getting their snacks
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,or they're going to\Nmiss Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh don't worry, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing could keep Pinkie\NPie from missing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Except\Nmaybe cotton candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Pinkie, the\Nshow's starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One second! Just a little bit\Nbigger, please, but hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:16:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing!\NShe's doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope this works!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope I'm not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pfft! I don't know what\Ntook that pony so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Rainbow Crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna tell us what\Njust happened, newbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I should hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You changed the routine\Nwithout consulting me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and put other\Nponies at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've drummed flyers out\Nof the Bolts for less.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I know and I'm ready for\Nwhatever punishment you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys were right to\Ncall me Rainbow Crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been\Na standout flier,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but since I joined\Nthe Wonderbolts,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only stood out\Nfor making mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been my\Ndream my whole life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess maybe I'm not\NWonderbolt material after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the most talented\Nflier we've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've saved all of\NEquestria like, a dozen times!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you're supposed\Nto be a Wonderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting\Nfor a spot to open up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since you\Njoined the Reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you guys... all\Ncalled me Rainbow Crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so? My\Nnickname's Clipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why they\Ncall me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, cause you're as\Nfast as a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I clipped my\Nwing on a flagpole
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as I was landing on\Nmy first day. Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:19:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Flatfoot. My first day I\Nmisjudged my landing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and came down right on\NSpitfire's hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowpoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoof 'n' Mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to know\Nwhat they call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that is\Nso much worse than Crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, does this mean I'm\Nstill on the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can be\Npart of this team
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and not constantly\Ntry to showboat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise. I spent my\Nwhole life trying to be
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a standout flier, but now\Nthat I'm a Wonderbolt,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's time to be OK\Nwith fitting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Because I really didn't\Nwant to miss the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to tease you for years about\Nthis catastrophe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that crash was epic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're on\Nprobation for a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Rainbow Dash, we just\Nwanted to check on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing great, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you don't need any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. This mess is my\Nresponsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've gotta clean it up\Nmyself. And after this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Spitfire's got me cleaning\Nthe Wonderbolts compound
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for the next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are you in\Nsuch a good mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Duh! Because I'm a Wonderbolt!
